description:
Digital chapters for the Hero House graphic novel.

When former teen hero Nate Hedges gets tapped by the university president to go undercover and investigate the Eps, will Nate be able to figure out who to trust and find a place where he finally belongs? Or will he have much bigger things to worry about than what his major should be...? Pledge allegiance to the next generation of comedic super-hero action, from writer Justin Aclin and artist Mike Dimayuga (Hack/Slash) and featuring a cover by the legendary Ed McGuinness (Hulk, Superman/Batman.)
name: Hero House
